Corey Della Pietra
CIS 4930 Assignment 3 

--------------------------------------------------

1. Run 'make' command to create the executable file 'NaiveBayes'

2. To use the classifier, execute:
	NaiveBayes <training_file> <test_file> 

3. Program will out the results of the classifier in the following format:
	(training file) TP FN FP TN
	(testing file)  TP FN FP TN

   Where TP = true positive
	 FN = false negative
	 FP = false positive
	 TN = true negative

4. Run 'make clean' command to delete executable, object file, and core dump
